      "content": "The purpose of this firm is to scale up an opposition research team to an industrial level. Generating hundreds or thousands of data points, connections, references, updating bot scrapings a day.\n\n## BotWrangler\nA programmer / researcher. Determines which online pages to scrape every day, does quality assurance on all subjects of bots to ensure data is still good, if data isn't, steps back data to its original state.\n\n## Digital Librarian /  Data Engineer\nEnsures the metadata is accurate, provides strategies to preserve and migrate data to new database frameworks as they develop. Must know Object Modeling language. Responsible for future proofing and ensuring metadata standards across the organization\n\n## Researcher level 1\n\nFirm would start with at least one researcher-- someone adept at business documents. Researcher 1's would be present at the start of the firm, determining schema and classifications of the data.\n\n## Researcher level 2 / Linguist\n\nResponsible for project based and subject matter specialties. Will require business level language of subject matter, familiarity with regional dialects and cultural subtexts.\n\n## Research Assistant\nFloater, responsible for background, various research oriented tasks.",
