      "content": "I make tools for people to think with. My main interest personally and professionally is in Graphesis, Graph Theory.",
      "date": "Mon 05 Mar 2018 11:27:43 AM PST",
      "grn": "a90955c9-14e8-44ee-8fcf-26bf59df5832",
      "id": "lindsey-mysse-introduction",
